# Rendered outputs from knit / quarto render — sources (.Rmd, .qmd) are the
# tracked artifacts; the rendered HTML, the knitr-intermediate .md, and the
# companion asset directories are regenerated locally and should not be
# committed.
#
# knitr produces `<basename>.md` (the intermediate markdown) and `figure/`
# (default chunk-plot output dir) next to the .Rmd; Quarto produces
# `<basename>_files/` next to the .qmd.
*.html
*.md
figure/
*_files/
